gravity.description: The value of gravity to use

defaultTap.description: Speed to set the ball to when it is tapped

impactEffect.description: The particle effect to trigger when the ball is tapped

ballMinimum.description: When ball goes below minimum y value game over is triggered

speedMult.description: Multiplier to apply to X speed when tap is off center

angMult.description: Multiplier to apply to angular speed when tap is off center

triggerActivated.description: Flag to track if the trigger has been activated for the current throw
